
Ranger Help for: barren
=======================

SUMMARY:    
The barren terrain is just that barren. Its not void of life, but you
would think it is if you ever saw it. In fact, Ranger's that live in
the barren environment never know what kind of follower they will get,
it could be anything. Due to its extreme nature, the Ranger population
in this terrain is the smallest, other than water terrains. Skills
use is limited here, and there aren't many areas in the realms that
are barren, athough there are a few.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: Individual terrains

